title: 현 상황
new-page: true
is-special: true
on-arrival: {!
Q.position = "";
if (Q.player_party == 'm') {
    if (Q.m_in_exco) {
        Q.position = 'Soviet Executive Committee';
        if (Q.m_in_gov) {
            Q.position += ', in government';
        }
    } else if (Q.m_in_gov) {
        Q.position = 'in government';
    } else {
        Q.position = 'in opposition';
    }
} else if (Q.player_party == 'b') {
    if (Q.b_in_exco) {
        Q.position = 'Soviet Executive Committee';
        if (Q.b_in_gov) {
            Q.position += ', in government';
        }
    } else if (Q.b_in_gov) {
        Q.position = 'in government';
    } else {
        Q.position = 'in opposition';
    }
} else if (Q.player_party == 'sr') {
    if (Q.sr_in_exco) {
        Q.position = 'Soviet Executive Committee';
        if (Q.sr_in_gov) {
            Q.position += ', in government';
        }
    } else if (Q.sr_in_gov) {
        Q.position = 'in government';
    } else {
        Q.position = 'in opposition';
    }
} else if (Q.player_party == 'k') {
    if (Q.k_in_gov) {
        Q.position += 'in government';
    } else {
        Q.position = 'in oppsition';
    }
}

// TODO: create a list of governing parties
Q.governing_parties = [];
if (Q.k_in_gov) {
    Q.governing_parties.push("Kadets");
}
if (Q.sr_in_gov) {
    Q.governing_parties.push("SRs");
}
if (Q.m_in_gov) {
    Q.governing_parties.push("Mensheviks");
}
if (Q.b_in_gov) {
    Q.governing_parties.push("Bolsheviks");
}
Q.governing_parties_str = Q.governing_parties.join(", ");

Q.exco_parties = [];

if (Q.m_in_exco) {
    Q.exco_parties.push("Mensheviks");
}
if (Q.defensist_in_exco) {
    Q.exco_parties.push("Menshevik-Defensists");
}
if (Q.internationalist_in_exco) {
    Q.exco_parties.push("Menshevik-Internationalists");
}
if (Q.sr_in_exco) {
    Q.exco_parties.push("SRs");
}
if (Q.left_sr_in_exco) {
    Q.exco_parties.push("Left-SRs");
}
if (Q.right_sr_in_exco) {
    Q.exco_parties.push("Right-SRs");
}
if (Q.b_in_exco) {
    Q.exco_parties.push("Bolsheviks");
}
if (Q.k_in_exco) {
    Q.exco_parties.push("Kadets");
}

Q.exco_parties_str = Q.exco_parties.join(", ");

Q.monthly_inflation_disp = Q.monthly_inflation.toFixed(1);
Q.inflation_disp = Q.inflation.toFixed(1);
Q.unemployed_disp = Q.unemployed.toFixed(1);
!}

= [+ player_party_name +] 현황

[+ year +]년 [+ month : month +]월 [+ week +]주차 

현재 지위: [+ position +]

사용 가능한 정당 자원:
[? if player_party == "b": [+ b_resources +] ?]
[? if player_party == "m": [+ m_resources +] ?]
[? if player_party == "k": [+ k_resources +] ?]
[? if player_party == "sr": [+ sr_resources +] ?]

당내 불만도:
[? if player_party == "b": [+ b_dissent_percent : dissent +] ?]
[? if player_party == "m": [+ m_dissent_percent : dissent +] ?]
[? if player_party == "k": [+ k_dissent_percent : dissent +] ?]
[? if player_party == "sr": [+ sr_dissent_percent : dissent +] ?]

= [+ government_form : government_form +]

총리: [+ prime_minister +] ([+ prime_minister_party +])

정부 참여 정당: [+ governing_parties_str +]

# Coalition dissent???

국가 예산: [+ budget +]

[? if not ca_election_held: 제헌의회 선거 일정: [? if ca_scheduled: [+ next_election_year +]년 [+ next_election_month : month +]월 [+ next_election_week +]주차로 예정 ?] [? if not ca_scheduled: 아직 일정이 잡히지 않았음 ?] ?]

[? if ca_election_held: 제헌의회 소집일: [+ ca_year +]년 [+ ca_month : month +]월 [+ ca_week +]주차 ?]

= 페트로그라드 소비에트

의장: [+ soviet_chair +] ([+ soviet_chair_party +])

집행위원회 구성 정당: [+ exco_parties_str +]

의석 전체 구성:
멘셰비키: [+ m_soviet +]%
볼셰비키: [+ b_soviet +]%
사회혁명당: [+ sr_soviet +]%
아나키스트: [+ anarchist_soviet +]%
기타: [+ other_soviet +]%
[? if defensist_split: 멘셰비키 방위주의파: [+ defensist_soviet_votes_dec +]% ?]
[? if internationalist_split: 멘셰비키 국제주의파: [+ internationalist_soviet_votes_dec +]% ?]
[? if right_sr_split: 우파 사회혁명당: [+ right_sr_soviet_votes_dec +]% ?]
[? if left_sr_split: 좌파 사회혁명당: [+ left_sr_soviet_votes_dec +]% ?]

= 평화

전쟁 진행 상황: [+ war_progress : war_score +]

[? if not is_armistice and not is_peace and armistice_progress: 휴전 협상 진행도: [+ armistice_progress +] ?]

[? if is_armistice: 현재 휴전 상태가 유지되고 있습니다. ?]

[? if is_armistice and not is_peace: 평화 협상 진행도: [+ central_negotiations +]?]

[? if allied_victory: 동맹국 측에서 휴전을 요청해 왔습니다. 이로써 전쟁이 종결되었습니다. ?]

전쟁 피로도: [+ war_weariness : war_weariness +]

군대 내 불안: [+ soldier_unrest : war_weariness +]

= 토지

토지 개혁 정책: [+ land_reform : land_reform +]

토지 개혁 진행도: [+ land_reform_progress : land_reform_progress +]

농촌 지역 불안: [+ rural_unrest : war_weariness +]

= 식량

# Real income (% of 1913): [+ income +]%
월간 인플레이션: [+ monthly_inflation +]% ([+ inflation +]% annually)

식량 부족 상황: [+ hunger : hunger +]

실업률: [+ unemployed +]%

노동계 불안: [+ labor_unrest : war_weariness +]





@politics
title: 정치
on-arrival: {!
Q.m_relation = 0;
Q.b_relation = 0;
Q.sr_relation = 0;
Q.k_relation = 0;
switch (Q.player_party) {
    case 'b':
        Q.b_relation = -1;
        Q.m_relation = Q.m_b_relation;
        Q.k_relation = Q.b_k_relation;
        Q.sr_relation = Q.b_sr_relation;
        break;
    case 'm':
        Q.m_relation = -1;
        Q.b_relation = Q.m_b_relation;
        Q.k_relation = Q.m_k_relation;
        Q.sr_relation = Q.m_sr_relation;
        break;
    case 'sr':
        Q.sr_relation = -1;
        Q.b_relation = Q.b_sr_relation;
        Q.m_relation = Q.m_sr_relation;
        Q.k_relation = Q.sr_k_relation;
        break;
    case 'k':
        Q.k_relation = -1;
        Q.b_relation = Q.b_k_relation;
        Q.m_relation = Q.m_k_relation;
        Q.sr_relation = Q.sr_k_relation;
        break;
}
!}

