임시정부에 대한 방침: [? if player_party = "m": [+ m_prov_gov_policy : prov_gov_policy +]?][? if player_party = "sr": [+ sr_prov_gov_policy : prov_gov_policy +]?][? if player_party = "k": [+ k_prov_gov_policy : prov_gov_policy +]?][? if player_party = "b": [+ b_prov_gov_policy : prov_gov_policy +]?]

