민족 문제 방침: [? if player_party = "m": [+ m_nationality_policy : nationality_policy +]?][? if player_party = "sr": [+ sr_nationality_policy : nationality_policy +]?][? if player_party = "k": [+ k_nationality_policy : nationality_policy +]?][? if player_party = "b": [+ b_nationality_policy : nationality_policy +]?]

